sk capital project shorenstein aparc project completed information and communication technology in rural india shorenstein aparc project completed introducing power pricing reforms in india shorenstein aparc project completed publications the 5 most recent are displayed more publications cover knowledge perspectives of new product development a comparative approach dimitris g assimakopoulos elias g carayannis rafiq dossani springer 2012 buy+ cover the changing governance of higher education in india martin carnoy rafiq dossani stanford university 2011 pdf+ cover the future of india's muslims rafiq dossani avicenna the stanford journal on muslim affairs vol 1 1 2011 html+ pdf+ cover social media in the workplace rafiq dossani stanford university 2011 pdf+ cover network associations and professional growth among engineers from india and china in silicon valley rafiq dossani ashish kumar american behavioral scientist vol 55 7 2011 html+ pdf+ events & presentations only 5 recent upcoming are displayed more events & presentations discourses of defiance framing muslim self determination in thailand and the philippines may 23 2012 shorenstein aparc seminar series joseph chinyong liow education and employment among muslims in india an analysis of patterns and trends may 16 2012 shorenstein aparc seminar series rakesh basant the political presence of india's muslims april 25 2012 shorenstein aparc seminar series wajahat habibullah comparing china's islams muslim minority accommodation to chinese rule april 13 2012 shorenstein aparc seminar series dru c gladney social media and the globalization of business may 25 2011 fsi stanford shorenstein aparc conference audio+ audio transcript available pdf+ 2 papers 2 presentations available search fsi search within everything courses events fellowships news op eds people publications research other pages research news experts gather to define a framework for smp research may 31 2011 shorenstein aparc sprie news rafiq dossani addresse